 KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO将SINSEKAI STUDIO重组为新系统https://p2y.jp/kamitsubaki-studio-reorganizes-merges-sinsekai-studio-into-new-organization/ https://p2y.jp/kamitsubaki-studio-reorganizes-merges-sinsekai-studio-into-new-organization/#respondp2y_admin Wed, 12 Jul 2023 09:11:55 +0000 VTuberバーチャルメタバース音楽KAMITSUBAKI STUDIOSINSEKAI STUDIOTHINKRXRYouTuberバーチャルYouTuberバーチャルシンガー https://p2y.jp/?p=96256 <p> 2023年7月11日，THINKR Co., Ltd.重组了虚拟歌手和创作者所属的KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO。姐妹工作室 SI [...]</p>后KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO重组SINSEKAI STUDIO并首次在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上<a href="https://p2y.jp/kamitsubaki-studio-reorganizes-merges-sinsekai-studio-into-new-organization/">合并到新系统</a>。; <p></p><p> 2023年7月11日，THINKR Co., Ltd.重组了虚拟歌手和创作者所属的<strong>KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO</strong> 。我们宣布通过整合姊妹工作室SINSEKAI STUDIO并增加新的创作者来建立新的系统。</p><p>此外，官方网站和工作室主标志的更新也被公布。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="96258" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/kamitsubaki-studio-reorganizes-merges-sinsekai-studio-into-new-organization/kamitsubaki_studio_reorganizes_merges_sinsekai_studio_into_new_organization/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kamitsubaki_studio_reorganizes_merges_sinsekai_studio_into_new_organization.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="kamitsubaki_studio_reorganizes_merges_sinsekai_studio_into_new_organization" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kamitsubaki_studio_reorganizes_merges_sinsekai_studio_into_new_organization.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kamitsubaki_studio_reorganizes_merges_sinsekai_studio_into_new_organization.png" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kamitsubaki_studio_reorganizes_merges_sinsekai_studio_into_new_organization.png" alt="KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO将SINSEKAI STUDIO重组为新系统" class="wp-image-96258"/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc-0McY2q0Sry9wVQ5JGEYobp96NQeQV3_TAKVgoefsGBiaiMbdFVYiojOYHq3QbXSNFMOK7tYQKlmEfI6zajiYepShvXU7vw1mLjKPxJxKvfmrt12svztZd7kGl0dnCZIpKy9rZum-hkAx4CE1_oNck=w1097-h557-s-no" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO</figcaption></figure><p>此次工作室重组中，将成立4个部门和4个新厂牌。此外，在品牌下，我们将设立“CREATOR FARM”新人才培养板块，新的创作者将参与其中。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">分配</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc93F9yZOpDfvdyvM_b81vfToMVFqAK7kG0xdDkWCzYyMUpUJsxoXIdgO0N-yElRXbNUZcPMjWztnrw0_XS2XRGJgQjfQte1jS6vSOG_xAcDU0x36w-j-0w6CuN3DYfpvq6tsccfzGf_RLw5anI7bpZd=w1097-h617-s-no" alt="" width="402" height="226"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO</figcaption></figure><ul><li>具有音乐厂牌和艺人管理功能的“KAMITSUBAKI LABEL”</li><li>专门负责原创故事开发的“神椿物语研究开发部”</li><li>专门从事Metaverse开发和XR体验开发的“Kantsubaki虚拟世界研究开发部”</li><li>负责开发KAMITSUBAKI商品的“神椿商品企划开发部” </li></ul><p></p><div class="nhxcw64af2586609c0" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
