re=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p>然后，你就可以把这部作品当作一个“可爱的操蛋游戏”来欣赏，把它的粗俗元素当作一个故事来欣赏，而开场电影中出现的所谓“无理吹老头”已经成为了一个网络迷因。当今吸引许多人关注的游戏软件，例如在“RTA in Japan”活动中玩的游戏。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="Enchant Romain -Power of Dark Side- - RTA 日本夏季赛 2022 年" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yPd6DJRiGCM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="gtyjs64af2586742ea" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
