</style><h3 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">《可爱的kusoge》衬托出才艺魅力</h3><p>索帕特拉（Suo Patra）是在ASMR发行界拥有顶级人气的艺人。他在VTuber行业拥有广泛的人脉关系，从各大机关、团体的人才到个人人才，受到很多人的仰慕。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[#VWW圆桌会议] VWW圆桌讨论[Patra Suo/Miu Tsukino/Rize Helesta/Sana Natori]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JmcdkxeVi_s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Miu Tsukino/Rize Helesta：© ANYCOLOR, Inc. </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【AC女子派对……！ ？ 】 当我向一位复古游戏前辈询问推荐游戏时，那是一片沼泽和地狱w" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DkTqAkTsfTM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p> 5月9日从VTuber办公室Nanashinku毕业，是未来活动备受关注的艺人之一。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="p34v3GV3VR"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-graduated-from-774inc-nanashiinku-and-became-independent/">VTuber Suo Patra 从 Nanashinku 毕业并独立</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Suo Patra 从 Nanashinku 毕业并独立” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-graduated-from-774inc-nanashiinku-and-became-independent/embed/#?secret=HoH9Z9ixvZ#?secret=p34v3GV3VR" data-secret="p34v3GV3VR" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p>而帕特拉小姐，作为脱离至今为止所属的经纪公司和团体，作为个人艺人的活动之一，于<strong>7</strong>月1日开始，这次将发行《古代特洛曼》的戏剧。<strong>事实上，我觉得这个分发内容是推荐给那些迄今为止还不了解Patra的人的。</strong> </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[Enchant Roman] 畅玩花费 20,000 日元购买的传奇 RPG！ #1【帕特拉索】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QjV98k2O8uk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[Enchant Roman] 畅玩花费 20,000 日元购买的传奇 RPG！ #2【帕特拉索】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/59dHFnql9NQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="robso64af258674392" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
